# DevKit Knowledge

Interactive help for the Cadre DevKit.

## Architecture

```
.cursor/
├── commands/    # Slash commands
├── rules/       # Domain expertise (skills)
├── hooks/       # Lifecycle automation
└── docs/        # Documentation
```

## Commands

| Command | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| `/greenfield` | New project discovery → SPEC, DESIGN, PLAN |
| `/plan` | Feature implementation planning |
| `/research` | Deep parallel research |
| `/backlog` | Document bugs/enhancements |
| `/review` | Code quality review |
| `/validate` | Automated checks |
| `/ship` | Git commit workflow |
| `/progress` | Save research as docs |
| `/slop` | Remove AI artifacts |
| `/learn` | This help system |

## Workflow

**New Project:**
```
/greenfield → /plan → implement → /review → /validate → /ship
```

**Existing Project:**
```
/plan → implement → /review → /validate → /ship
```

